column2:
Depression Questions  :
In the past week, I couldn't seem to experience any positive feeling at all.
column3: I'm constantly comparing myself to others. It makes me feel like a failure.
column4: I felt that I had nothing to look forward to.
column5: I was unable to become enthusiastic about anything.
column6: I felt I wasn't worth much as a person.
column7: I felt that life was meaningless.
column9:
Anxiety Questions: 
I was aware of dryness of my mouth.
column10: I experienced breathing difficulty (e.g., excessively rapid breathing, breathlessness in the absence of physical exertion).
column11: I experienced trembling (e.g., in the hands).
column12: I was worried about situations in which I might panic and make a fool of myself.
column13: I was aware of the beating of my heart in the absence of physical exertion.
column14: I felt scared without any good reason.
column15:
Stress Questions :
I found myself getting agitated.
column16: I was intolerant of anything that kept me from getting on with what I was doing.
column17: I found it difficult to relax.
column18: I felt that I was using a lot of nervous energy.
column19: I found myself getting impatient when I was delayed in any way.
